title: GDG DevFest 2015 Announced
brief: Baroda GDG is proud to announce the second annual GDG DevFest - the largest Google related event in Gujarat. Like last year, the event will be held on 1st November in Baroda. So aside all your business at this time and book tickets to the cultural capital of Gujarat.

title: Call for Speakers
brief: We're very excited - not just because of the inordinate amount of caffeine based products consumed - but also because our team are putting together the final missing parts to the biggest Google related event in Gujarat - GDG DevFest : Baroda 2015.
